x = PseudoVADD&#95;V&#95;V&#95;M1 passthru, a, b, vl1, sew, policy y = PseudoVMV&#95;V&#95;V&#95;M1 passthru, x, vl2, sew, policy (where vl1 &lt;= vl2, see related tryToReduceVL)

-&gt;

y = PseudoVADD&#95;V&#95;V&#95;M1 passthru, a, b, vl1, sew, policy
